{"tid":626963,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好意思 想問嘢","createTime":"2018-04-12T14:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T14:41:49.000Z","uid":11955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d01351fca2d8d0ab4fd84cfd347ecc4c4a346bcb","tid":626963,"uid":11955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"好耐之前係唔知連登定高登睇過一堆故事<br />\n但依家搵唔返<br />\n關於係有個網站 唔肯定係咪Riddit<br />\n講唔同既怪物<br />\n<br />\n記得有好多<br />\n其中一個係講有間房 入面有隻怪物<br />\n要三個人入去負責清理間房<br />\n其中一個人一定要用眼望住隻怪物對眼 <br />\n咁隻怪物就會企係度唔郁<br />\n然後視線一離開左隻嘢之後 隻嘢就會殺人<br />\n整斷人條頸咁<br />\n<br />\n想搵返d故事黎睇 有無人記得/知<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b8d842c3fade234dbad7617d0e9ceb12599e6e","tid":626963,"uid":21460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"scp foundation<br />\n可以自己上wiki睇下<br />\n你講嗰隻係SCP-173 (SCP即係啲怪物)<br />\n唔同scp都有唔同故事，不過SCP-173出名啲"},{"pid":"7dea9f230b5172f03e69137297818cb389c7b75f","tid":626963,"uid":21460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.scp-wiki.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scp-wiki.net%2F&d=barE%2FgOtKSgBVCbrlwDp0ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=18389e2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.scp-wiki.net/</a>"},{"pid":"2fc75fdf704a7a8342281b09b0966e11cbfaca64","tid":626963,"uid":11955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1b8d842c3fade234dbad7617d0e9ceb12599e6e","tid":626963,"uid":21460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"scp foundation<br />\n可以自己上wiki睇下<br />\n你講嗰隻係SCP-173 (SCP即係啲怪物)<br />\n唔同scp都有唔同故事，不過SCP-173出名啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"thanks！其實就係搵唔到關鍵字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj